VERSION 0.2.1
- Changed Milestone structure in DB.
- Create and implemented sub-sub-blocks of `todo_detail_block` for `Todo` module.
- Changed the UI of `todo_detail_block`.
- Added state management for `todo_detail_block`.
- Created sub-sub-blocks for `todo_list_block` for `Todo` module.

VERSION: 0.2.0
- Made some project restructuring for better understandibility.
- Created `state management system` for the application. It has three main states: `app_control` (to facilitate global application level control), `block_control` (to facilitate block level control), and `sub_block_control` (to facilitate module level control).
- Added UP/DOWN navigation.
- Added `global` (app level) and `local` (sub-block level) navigations.
- Added state related keybindings.
- Added `select` a block and `exit` a block functionality.
- Added sub-block level navigation for `Todo` module.